jobInfo.postDescription:
Main Responsibility 主要工作职责
1. Analysis of customer requirements and preparation of solutions within the 
framework of customer orders and /or product/solution development
分析客户需求，在客户订单和/或产品/解决方案开发的框架内准备解决方案
2. Definition and documentation of the scope of works/services required by the 
customer in accordance with the sales department and guidance of team leader
根据销售部门和团队领导的指导，定义并记录客户要求的工作/服务范围
3. Processing, maintenance and conditioning data for customers according to the 
requirement of projects
根据项目要求为客户处理、维护、调整数据
4. Participate in the establishment and update of the auto parts database to improve 
the accuracy of parts adaptation
参与汽车零部件数据库的建立和更新，提高零部件适配的准确性
5. Cooperation with other corporate divisions like VDS, PADS, Sales, Product etc.
与公司其他部门合作，如 VDS,PADS,销售,产品等
6. Assist the leader and overseas colleagues to complete projects
协助领导和海外同事完成项目
7. Other tasks assigned by leader
领导交办的其他工作
Qualification 任职要求
• Bachelor degree or above
本科及以上学历
• Proficient in Excel/Access/VBA and formula processing operations, Familiar with 
Python/SQL/Power BI and understand how to apply it in data scenarios;
精通 Excel/Access/VBA,熟练掌握相关公式处理操作; 熟悉 Python/SQL/Power BI，了解
如何在数据场景运用；
• Experienced in data processing is preferred; Priority given to those with relevant data 
knowledge of automotive spare parts;
有数据处理经验者优先，具备汽车零部件相关数据知识者优先
• Good knowledge about customer specific product management tasks in the IAM area 
(Independent Automotive Aftermarket) will be an added advantage;
熟悉 IAM 领域(独立汽车售后市场)客户特定产品管理工作优先考虑；
• A positive attitude, curious,self-motivated and takes responsibility;
态度积极，好奇心强，自驱力，责任心强；
• Strong logical analysis ability, good communication and customer oriented.
具有较强的逻辑分析能力，良好的沟通能力和客户引导能力。
• A quick leaner and team player
能够快速学习和良好的团队合作能力

您一旦申请泰案联职位，即表示您授权泰案联使用您的个人信息用于招聘相关的活动，并保存在泰案联的招聘系统或数据库中。我们将根据泰案联全球隐私政策对您的个人信息予以负责任的管理、使用与保护。

brandComInfo.introduce:
As a full-service provider of data, services and processes, we are already market leaders in Europe and are rapidly expanding this advantage worldwide. At TecAlliance, technology and automotive specialists collaborate to digitalise & shape the future of the automotive aftermarket. We owe our growing success to simple principles like openness, courage, passion, curiosity, selflessness, innovation, inclusion and integrity. It is the embodiment of these traits that makes TecAlliance the driving force behind the digitalisation of the entire market. It is also what we look for in new employees.
泰案联（TecAlliance）成立于1994年，前身为德国泰多克（TecDoc），其致力于为汽车后市场提供标准化的数据和服务，其泰多克标准（TecDoc Standard）已成为全球汽车零部件售后行业公认的数据标准，代表着权威的数据质量认证。其产品和服务遍及全球140多个国家，拥有超过1400个配件品牌的880万配件信息，是具有30多年专业经验国际品牌。
泰案联中国作为德国TecAlliance GmbH的全资子公司于2006年进入中国市场以来发展迅速，主要业务是为汽车独立售后市场提供泰多克（TecDoc）、泰捷云（TecCom）以及TecRMI三大类产品和一站式服务, 具体包括车型及配件查询、电子订单处理以及维修保养信息等一系列解决方案。
泰案联是汽车售后市场零部件数据和业务解决方案的全球市场标杆，能够帮助企业以数据为导向做出决策，并提高协作效率，扩展全球业务。
Working at TecAlliance: Driving the future of digitization for the mobility eco-system.
